title: BONUS 2 - Alien Extravaganza! Roswell, Area 51, UFOs and more!
description: When did humans first claim to be contacted by extraterrestrials? What really happened at Roswell? What is going on at Area 51? Why do aliens want to stick things in our butts? Is it all made up!?! Take a listen to a thoroughly researched (and very sarcastic) investigation into whether or not we've made contact with outer space.
author: dan@dancummins.tv (Dan Cummins)
